an parliament or by the joint member state government a it be now the maastricht treaty allow subject of member state to stand for election in another member state they be reside in do you think you would or could vote for a foreigner if idea appeal to you do you think mep should be allow to be a member of a national parliament or a regional parliament too or a member of a national or regional government body the european parliament now ha meet in both strasbourg and brussel mep themself be for a complete move to brussel in great majority but political compromise between the government of the member state stick to the statu quo do you approve of thi or do you think the european parliament should meet in one city only and if ye which please post ymy answer to to which all followup be automatically direct if you do not have acces to that group please mail ymy answer directly to me and i will post it for you i hope many of you will take the time to post their view on thi matter roland siebelink lokaal centrum voor de studie van nieuwe vrije universiteit brussel medium informatie en telecommunicatie pleinlaan brussel belgium tel direkt e-mail rcsiebel tel centrum talk rcsiebel fax centrum 